%dl
  %dt Usage
  %dd
    %p You can post a message with <code>source</code> parameter like below:
    %pre $ curl --data-urlencode &quot;source=hello, world&quot;

    %p You can also use HTML format:
    %pre $ curl --data-urlencode &quot;source=&lt;h1&gt;hi&lt;/h1&gt;&quot; -d format=html {{endpoint}}

    %p Additionally, you can post image with <code>image</code> parameter:
    %pre $ curl --form image=@/path/to/image.png {{endpoint}}
